Package zserio.runtime.pubsub

This package contains classes for Zserio Pub/Sub.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PubsubCallback<T>
    Generic callback invoked by generated Pub/Sub classes on subscriptions.
    PubsubInterface
    Interface for Pub/Sub client backends.
    PubsubInterface.Callback
    Callback passed to the subscribe method and called when a message with subscribed topic arrives.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    PubsubException
    Exception thrown when an error in Pub/Sub occurs.
